<BR><BR>
<STRONG>Optical Cable Corporation manufactures and
 markets a broad range of fiber optic
cables for "high bandwidth" transmission of data,
video and audio communications over moderate distances.
  Optical Cable Corporation's cables can be used
both indoors and outdoors and utilize a
tight-buffered coating that protects each optical fiber.</strong>
